OL,3,CMan arrested after drugs, guns and
OL,4,Cammunition found during security alert
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof drug and firearm offences following
OL,8,Fa security alert in north Belfast.
OL,10,FThe PSNI conducted a search of a home
OL,11,Fat Rosapenna Parade following the
OL,12,Falert on Friday.
OL,14,FOn Saturday, police said the operation
OL,15,Fhad ended and announced they had
OL,16,Frecovered suspected firearms,
OL,17,Fammunition, drugs and cash.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
