OL,3,CMan arrested after drugs, guns and
OL,4,Cammunition found during security alert
OL,6,FA 28-year-old man was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of a number of offences
OL,8,Fincluding possession of a class A
OL,9,Fcontrolled drug with intent to supply,
OL,10,Fpossessing a firearm and ammunition in
OL,11,Fsuspicious circumstances and
OL,12,Fpossessing ammunition without a
OL,13,Fcertificate.
OL,15,FHe has since been released on bail as
OL,16,Fpolice inquiries continue.
OL,18,FDetectives appealed to anyone with
OL,19,Finformation to contact them in
OL,20,FMusgrave on 101, quoting reference
OL,21,Fnumber 133 17/07/26.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/3
